data.description: Don't miss out on this stunning ranch-style home with an inviting open concept layout. It is ready for you to move in and start enjoying. The spacious family room boasts a vaulted ceiling, while the entire home features beautiful laminate wood flooring. The attention to detail is evident in the finished trim and woodwork. The kitchen is a chef's dream with custom cabinets and beautiful lighting. Natural light floods the home through large windows, creating a bright and airy atmosphere. With 3 bedrooms and 2 full baths, including a generous master bedroom with a large walk-in closet, there is plenty of space for everyone! All stainless steel appliances are included, and the convenience of a washer and dryer is also provided.
